{"tid":1290442,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"乃木坂46討論區#195：最近好似幾多成員體調不良","createTime":"2019-07-06T13:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T15:01:08.000Z","uid":61389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4f8dd818e2540aa4c4a44247bbe0248a63d5471c","tid":1290442,"uid":61389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:21:38.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">LIHKG乃PO呼籲：<br />\n一期睇得一次得一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span><br />\n</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XgvGUH6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXgvGUH6.png&h=02202bfa&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46(Nogizaka46)</span> 是一個日本大型女子偶像團體，為另一著名女子團體AKB48的「官方對手／正式對手」（公式ライバル），因此其行銷策略與AKB48的姐妹團體&mdash;&mdash;SKE48、NMB48、HKT48等不同，但總製作人同樣是秋元康，且與其他姊妹團體之間仍常有跨團體的合作或競賽企畫。團體名字中的「46」讀作「Forty-six／フォーティシックス」，而不是讀作「四十六／よんじゅうろく」。包含一期生,二期生,三期生以及四期生在內，團體目前共有46名成員，而隊長為櫻井玲香。<br />\n乃木坂46是作為AKB48的「官方對手」而成立的女子團體，因此跟AKB48的「姊妹團體」（如SKE48等）不同。例如團體不像AKB48及其姊妹團體般擁有AKB48劇場、NMB48劇場等專屬表演場地。團體名稱中的「乃木坂」是唱片公司日本索尼音樂（SME）總部大樓的所在地。<br />\n根據秋元康所說，<span style=\"color: red;\">「46」象徵：「就算人數比AKB48少，也具有不遜於AKB48的幹勁</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">成員名單:</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nogizaka46.com/member/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nogizaka46.com%2Fmember%2F&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zRZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=c3dbd024\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nogizaka46.com/member/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">-NEWS-</div><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">乃木坂46 23rdシングル<br />\n「Sing Out！」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0cipwn6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0cipwn6.jpg&h=c51edcbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乃木坂46 4thアルバム<br />\n「今が思い出になるまで」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LdMnh3x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLdMnh3x.jpg&h=f6ef5b5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">斉藤優里1st写真集「7秒のしあわせ」 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UEdWQYN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUEdWQYN.png&h=e5c86eda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">映畫「Hot Gimmick: Girl Meets Boy」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">6月28日上映</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5XcXAn7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5XcXAn7.jpg&h=de229448&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">『いつのまにか、ここにいる Documentary of 乃木坂46』<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">7月5日上映</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uujOG31.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuujOG31.png&h=445c7414&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46成員列表 23RD VER.(最新)</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vaCRpX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vaCRpX.png&h=006e8631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46 四期生</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NjUnHMj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNjUnHMj.jpg&h=61687ed4&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎新人加入</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://nogizaka46-dc.com/sort/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnogizaka46-dc.com%2Fsort%2F&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zRZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=05ccf228\" target=\"_blank\">http://nogizaka46-dc.com/sort/</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請新/舊手足定期體檢，以便加入DD黨</span></span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Q&amp;A</div></span></span><br />\n1）那乃木坂乃何許人也？<br />\n簡單來說，乃木坂是來自日本的偶像組合，演戲唱歌跳舞等全部都會參與，是正統全能型偶像。<br />\n<br />\n2）那裡可以購買乃木坂既有關產品（生寫、CD、海報、寫真集、演唱會等）？<br />\n一般來說，信和地庫會有存貨，不過價錢就...另外有不少商品需於官方WEBSHOP購入，不過這裡有機會提供代購,，要看看手足們的心情。<br />\n<br />\n3）這裡可否討論其他非46的成員？<br />\n我們一般不會阻止，但請適量討論。皆因這裡主要討論46GRP,你也可作理性討論，攻擊、黑其他成員,但請先作好世界大戰的準備。<br />\n<br />\n4）那麼我要如何見到乃木坂成員？<br />\n直接飛去日本參加握手會、演唱會，但不要幻想他會再來港，因香港已經柒出國際。詳細辦法請向手足查詢。<br />\n<br />\n5）除了46GRP,有什麼值得推薦？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fJHNpRY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfJHNpRY.jpg&h=f4a670a8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0bxd4QW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0bxd4QW.gif&h=608c8129&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hPdEGos.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhPdEGos.gif&h=db4ab5fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TEMPLATE:</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ns1NdRm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNs1NdRm.png&h=61cb3eef&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"97d4bcb1014557f5d4225f7d86641c045880ae06","tid":1290442,"uid":61389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:22:25.000Z","msg":"乃木坂46討論區#194：真夏の全国ツアー2019 名古屋站<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1281327\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1281327</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"08d2fe18f34b2a71a4f600ec2d7202980322bc75","tid":1290442,"uid":65481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:31:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R1aWJEV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR1aWJEV.jpg&h=25924ce2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba57f4583e9c2ceb07983b95bc428da80018ace7","tid":1290442,"uid":61389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:20:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.nogizaka46.com/news/2019/07/-77-1.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nogizaka46.com%2Fnews%2F2019%2F07%2F-77-1.php&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zRZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=1f54f24d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.nogizaka46.com/news/2019/07/-77-1.php</a><br />\n純奈、日奈子體調不良<br />\n久保家族有事<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce95333a6076ed8ceeb9d865b8ca70ecd4ce6e9","tid":1290442,"uid":156861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T02:59:37.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"dd052df039c291fc764859a6d5bb0667a40905da","tid":1290442,"uid":6696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T15:01:08.000Z","msg":"新po 留名<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2edmiP1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2edmiP1.png&h=d794e4f5&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}